<p>Hampi is a village located in the state of Karnataka, India. It was once the It was once the capital of the Vijayanagara Empire and has many historical monuments and temples. Some of the notable places to visit in Hampi include the Virupaksha Temple, the Hampi Bazaar, and the Lotus Mahal.</p>
